00:41:26.210 --> 00:41:28.290
versus building divide.

00:41:28.290 --> 00:41:33.050
Don't think so if we invest
in these big iconic things,

00:41:33.050 --> 00:41:36.500
then that'll help and
attract attention to so on.

00:41:40.130 --> 00:41:41.420
Big iconic things are fine.

00:41:41.420 --> 00:41:44.570
I have no problem with
big iconic things,

00:41:44.570 --> 00:41:51.690
but investing in design at
all levels is important.

00:41:51.690 --> 00:41:54.350
But it's not just that, I'm
not saying that architects

00:41:54.350 --> 00:41:57.680
are heroes because
a lot of architects

00:41:57.680 --> 00:41:59.510
